Contents of Exercise Directory
==============================


plot_solution.py:
    a python3 script which will plot the outputs the code generates.

solution/
    directory containing correct versions of the linear advection code.
    Includes notes on what bugs were introduced on purpose for the exercise.
    You should be able to compile and run the codes, and to compare the
    expected results with your own.

src/
    source files for the code to be debugged as an exercise. Both a C and
    a fortran version exist.

theory/
    contains TeX files that explain a bit what the code is supposed to be doing.
